es|Futsal]] || 2007, 2011\u20132013, 2017\n|-\n| [[Golf at the Southeast Asian Games|Golf]] || 1985\u20131997, 2001, since 2005\n|-\n| [[Gymnastics at the Southeast Asian Games|Gymnastics]] || 1979\u20131981, 1985\u20131997, <br />2001\u20132007, 2011, since 2015\n|-\n| style=\"background: #D3D3D3;\" |[[Handball]] || 2005\u20132007\n|-\n| [[Beach handball at the Southeast Asian Games|Beach handball]] || Since 2019\n|-\n| [[Ice hockey at the Southeast Asian Games|Ice hockey]] || Since 2017\n|-\n| [[Indoor hockey at the Southeast Asian Games|Indoor hockey]] || Since 2017\n|-\n| [[Ju-jitsu at the Southeast Asian Games|Ju-jitsu]] || Since 2019\n|-\n| [[Judo at the Southeast Asian Games|Judo]] || 1967\u20131997, since 2001\n|-\n| [[Karate]] || 1985\u20131991, 1995\u20131997, <br />2001\u20132013, 2017\n|-\n| style=\"background: #D3D3D3;\" |[[Kenp\u014d]] || 2011\u20132013\n|}\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! Sport || Years\n|-\n| [[Kickboxing at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games|Kickboxing]] || Since 2019\n|-\n| [[Kurash at the Southeast Asian Games|Kurash]] || Since 2019\n|-\n| [[Lawn bowls at the Southeast Asian Games|Lawn bowls]] || 1997, 2001, 2005\u20132007, Since 2017\n|-\n| style=\"background: #D3D3D3;\" | Modern pentathlon || Since 2019\n|-\n| [[Muay thai at the Southeast Asian Games|Muay thai]] || 2005\u20132009, 2013, Since 2019\n|-\n| [[Netball at the Southeast Asian Games|Netball]] || 2001, since 2015\n|-\n| [[Obstacle racing at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games|Obstacle racing]] || Since 2019\n|-\n| style=\"background: #D3D3D3;\" | [[Paragliding at the 2011 Southeast Asian Games|Paragliding]] || 2011 only\n|-\n| [[Pencak silat at the Southeast Asian Games|Pencak silat]] || 1987\u20131989, 1993\u20131997, <br />since 2001\n|-\n| [[P\u00e9tanque at the Southeast Asian Games|P\u00e9tanque]] || Since 2001\n|-\n| [[Polo at the Southeast Asian Games|Polo]] || 2007, Since 2017\n|-\n| style=\"background: #D3D3D3;\" | [[Roller sports at the 2011 Southeast Asian